"Setting the cost to taxpayers on the basis of estimates for the reimbursement rates is highly misleading," said Walters.
'These estimates include staff, maintenance and many other hidden costs included in the annual funds'.
According to a 2015 RAND study, the reimbursement rates for DoD do not include personnel costs, but consider the costs of fuel, maintenance, and contract signing.
At that time, the former White House press officer, Sean Spicer, defended the helicopter ’ s use for the event.
